Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ We\N♪ Are the Crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Gems
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ We'll always save the day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Steven: ♪ And if you think\Nwe can't, we'll ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Always find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ That's why the people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Of this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Garnet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Amethyst
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ And Pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头显然非常高兴\NOnion sure was having a phenomenal time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,和史蒂文在沙发上蹦跶\Njumping with Steven on his couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但蹦了两个小时后\NBut after two hours of jumping,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他决定是时候结束了\Nhe decided that it was time to perhaps stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然后去做点别的？\Nand do something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，洋葱头打算吃点零食\NAh, so Onion decided he wanted a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他知道他可以随意\NAnd he knew he could help himself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,享用史蒂文厨房里的任何东西\Nto {\i1}anything{\i} {\i1}in Steven's kitchen.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,包括史蒂文的限量版薯片...\N[ Sighs ] Including Steven's favorite limited edition chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头闻了闻薯片\NOnion smelled the chip,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在鉴赏那极致气息\Nsavoring its delicious aroma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但没有零食能满足\NBut no snack could satisfy his hunger...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他对潜力的渴望\Nfor power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你爸爸回家了？\NOh, looks like you're dad's home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜本集“洋葱头的传说”\NI guess this round of "Onion Tales"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,该结束了。\Nhas come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再见！\NSee ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,结语\NEpilogue --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头不得不面对孤独\Nthings get a little lonely for Onion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不认识任何同龄伙伴\Nnot knowing any other kids his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但好在他有史蒂文\NBut luckily he had his friend Steven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一个愿意花时间陪伴“留守儿童”的人\Nwho would kindly donate some time to a youth in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来啦！\NComing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，洋葱头\NOh, Onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,又想找人玩玩？\NNeed someone to hang out with again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\NCome on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈\NOh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头想进门，但在门外被拦住了，\NOnion wanted to come in, but he paused in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要拖鞋，但不知道怎么脱\NHe needed to take his shoes off, but he didn't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去别的地方？\NYou want to go somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，维达利亚！你好，黄鳍-噫-噫\NHi, Vidalia! Hi, Yellowta-a-a-ail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚跑过了你家，洋葱头！\NW-We just ran past your house, Onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.55,0:02:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你要带我去哪？\NWhere are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪？\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知带你能吹口哨！\NI didn't know you could whistle like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NIs someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,鹰嘴豆\NGarbanzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，你们是很么人？\NAah! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们缓慢怪异的步伐让我很不舒服！\NYour slow and eerie approach is making me uncomfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊啊啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头，快跑！\NOnion, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看来史蒂文-宇宙该退场了\NLooks like it's curtains for Steven Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头，啊？\NOnion, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识这些人吗，洋葱头?\NUh, do you know these guys, Onion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,, 噢，他们是你的朋友！\NOh, they're your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，我的名字是史蒂文\NUh, my name's Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,鹰嘴豆\NGarbanzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜，你是鹰嘴豆？\NI guess, you're Garbanzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到你以豆子起名\NSince you're named after a bean
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你背上的宝宝一定叫...\Nthen the baby on your back must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,花豆？\NPinto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字是...\NAnd your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，笋瓜！ \NOh, Squash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在我左边是...\NAnd to my left, we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,弹弓？\N Slingshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...锅盖头？\N Uh, pot hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太清楚...\N Uh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,特-昂-汤？\NS-- S-S-Soup
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,呼～很高兴认识你们！\NWhew!  It's nice to meet all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,多么温馨的迎接！\NWhat a warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，我钱包！\NH-Hey, that's my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头，我一直以为你是个孤独的小男孩\NOnion, this whole time I thought you were just a lonely boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但你有一屋子朋友\NBut you have a whole pantry of friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你带我来这里\NThanks for bringing me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,鹰嘴豆\N Garbanzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,酷！一个肥皂箱做的Derby Car（手工制作的玩具车）\NCool! A soap-box derby car thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮一把吗？\NCan I lend you all a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,鹰嘴豆\N Garbanzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这安全吗？\NIs that safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,鹰嘴豆\NGarbanzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来超棒！\NThis looks amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的下吗？\NIs there enough room for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，出发！\N All right, let's roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能爬陡坡！\NIt even goes up steep hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,飘～\NSwerve-y!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,鹰嘴豆\N Garbanzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...发生了什么？\NUh... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！他不会有事吧？就只是撞了一下！\NWait! He's gonna be okay, right? It was just a little spill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是真的吗？\NIs this... really happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，花豆...我不知道该说什么...\NOh, Pinto... I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切发生的太突然了\NThis is all happened so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我-我去找救护人员！\NI-I'll call a medical professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个奇迹！花豆有治愈...能力？\NIt's a miracle! Pinto has healing pow...ers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你又捅我，又眨眼，就像这都是...\NW-Why'd you nudge me and wink like this was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,套路？\Na big joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--我明白了。嘿，这都是套路\NI -- I get it. Heh. G-Good joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们...你们真的骗过我了。\NHmm. Y'all -- Y'all really got me with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，真是个肥大的风衣！\NWhoa! That is a huge trench coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们打算拿来做什么？\NWhat're you gonna do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你们打算伪装成大人？\NYou're gonna pretend to be grown?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我能跟你们一起吗？\NCan I pretend with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,天，我们看起来太成年了！\NMan, we look so grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先做什么？\NWhat should we do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,买辆车？出入豪华旅馆(？\NBuy a car? Stay in a fancy hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,投票？\NVote?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，那不是行李山姆吗？\NHey, is that Suitcase Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得如果我们突然撞见他，他会对我们说“先生”？\NYou think if we bump into him, he'll call us "sir?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那会很有趣！\NThat would be funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？我们是这么做吗？\NOh, are we doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，行李山姆先生！\N Hello, Suitcase Sam, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是我，你的忠实顾客，成人先生！\NIt is I, your faithful customer, Mister Mature Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\N Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N W-Why'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,天...\NMan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为当我们没在一起玩时\NI always thought when we weren't hanging out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是一个人坐在栈道上，洋葱头\Nyou were just sitting alone on the boardwalk, Onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切从什么时候开始的？\NHow long has this been going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？只是在土里画画？\NWhat's going on over here? Just drawing in the dirt, Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这很好，一点也不吓人\NThat's cool, that's not creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对，汤汤？\NRight, Soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...好吧\NUh...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该,,,噢，好吧\NWhat should I-- Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是...个比赛吗？\NIs this...a race?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你,,,你们在赛虫？\NY-You're racing bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思！\N That's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住啊! 你能做到的! 不要停!\NCome on!You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,呼！我赢了！\NWhoo-hoo! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,给我的？谢谢！\NFor me? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？你们想让我...\NWhat? You want me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但...但它赢了啊！\NBut -- But he won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我...\NI...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到！\NI can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,虫子也许很怪，但我不想杀死它！\NBugs may be weird, but I don't want to kill one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我得回家了!\N I'm sorry. I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还好！\N All right. Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再有奇怪的朋友了，我看看...\NNo more weirdo friends. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我赌我亲亲的康妮有空\NI bet my best friend Connie is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，康妮！是我，史蒂文！\NHey, Connie! It's me, Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我--我在想你是否有...\NI -- I was wondering if you --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...不，并没有什么任务。我只想和你在一起～\NUm, no, th-there's no mission, I wanted to hang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你要进行返校采购？\NYou gotta do back to school shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，好吧\NOh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,替我向铅笔们问好。\NSay hi to the pencils for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我想佩迪应该愿意出来玩玩\NWell, I bet Peedee wants to hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[我没法出来玩。暑期最后加班]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,算了\NNo big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人有空吧？\NI-I'm sure someone else is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没有同龄好伙伴的孤独少男...\NLooks like the lonely boy with no friends his age
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是...\Nwas actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文\NSteven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不，洋葱头!我想静静！\NNo, Onion! Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用再陪我玩了\NYou don't have to play with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不，洋葱头!\N No, Onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头，听我说！\N Onion, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想通了！\NI figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我玩的唯一原因\NThe only reason you hang out with me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是你同情我，对吧？\Nis 'cause you feel bad for me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要撒谎来安慰我！\NYou don't have to lie to me to protect my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那些在树林中的孩子们？\NThose kids out there in the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们了解彼此，甚至无需言语！\NYou understand each other and you don't even talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是你真正的朋友！\NThey're your real friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以走吧！\NSo just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你可怜我！\NI don't need you to pity me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我一个人能做的\NThat's the one thing I can do by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，你是...你是比赛的获胜者\NHey, you're -- you're the winner of the bug race.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！洋葱头！我对不起！\NWait! Onion! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱头，等等我！\NOnion, wa-a-ait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们，对不起！都怪我！\NGuys, I'm sorry! It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是那个孤独的人！我--\NI was the lonely boy! I --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，到底怎么了？\NHey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等等...\NWait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是...\Nare you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要走吗？\Nleaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起之前表现的非常怪异！\NI'm sorry about being weirded out before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没必要走啊！\NYou don't have to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我--我知道了\NI-I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你们只在夏天到beach city来\NYou guys only come to Beach City during the summer months.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在秋天来了\NAnd since the fall is starting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们该准备回家了\Nit must be time for you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该说什么。我--\NI don't know what to say. I --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！谢谢你们让我一起玩！\NAww! Thanks for letting me hangout with you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都很棒！\NYou're all swell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再见！我永远不会忘记你们的！\NGoodbye! I'll never forget you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...那就是你为什么那么想让我回到这里\NSo, that's why you wanted me to come back here so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你最后的机会\NThis was your last chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,和你所有的朋友在一起\Nto have all your friends in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,噢...洋葱头非常伤心\NUh... Onion felt really sad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他夏天的伙伴都走了\Nabout his summer friends leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他又好过了一点\Nthen, he started to feel a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他想起了与朋友的所有美好时光\NHe remembered all the great times he had with his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,和一起搞的事情！\Nand all the cool stuff they did together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假再临前\NAnd until next summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他还有好朋友史蒂文一起玩\Nhe had his pal Steven to hangout with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他愿意\Ni-if he wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,噢...伙计...\N Aww, buddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer of Steven 放送完毕！终于追上进度。。【倒地
